da1","tid":325191,"uid":2207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:11:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>駁唔到啦，其實本身已經喺神枱，攞埋今個溫布頓再由神枱上多級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已經唔知可以點形容<br />\n<br />\n利申：拿度fans</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢見自己有傷 個態唔好<br />\n寧願抖一排<br />\n再出黎竟然好似仲勁左咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁樣調整返自己 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n溫網仲要一個set 都無輸 ...<br />\n真係好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e40ea8ec1ac186737c2c845eee3a62fe524495e","tid":325191,"uid":4957,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:13:45.000Z","msg":"阿朗-足球之神"},{"pid":"5ccb02cf0fe9dfccdb3ed995a590d40f4dfcd14a","tid":325191,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:21:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>阿朗-足球之神</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n稅務之神<br />\n慈善之神"},{"pid":"5b9b638fee526ffa397cb69db80f4b3fa6060e15","tid":325191,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:21:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>細威就係眾神之神</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大威呢咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細威&gt;大威"},{"pid":"43dec299e886419d149772be666e35458d14d243","tid":325191,"uid":54025,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:41:32.000Z","msg":"首先，籃球之神係kd"},{"pid":"3ef4ff20664fbda1d60980a89b18e1468633d4b0","tid":325191,"uid":24697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:46:47.000Z","msg":"森柏斯<br />\n亞加斯是什麼神"},{"pid":"a80586ea8ce8813e18e4bba8385955ee0811ac2b","tid":325191,"uid":2207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:53:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>森柏斯<br />\n亞加斯是什麼神</blockquot